      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是OpenRouter + Models。然后这一层下面挂两个东西：一个是Ai Agent LangGraph，另一个是——等等，LangGraph下面还要再展开两个子模块，Eliza角色模块和Langfuse遥测。",
      "elements_involved": [
