    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "统计比较简单，就一个GoogleAnalytics。重点是ClerkAuth认证这块，它下面要拆两条线：一条是TarifPlans走StripePayment，另一条是UserProfile，里面包含Credit Balance、Settings，还有ChatHistory+Supabase。",
      "elements_involved": [
